snippet.title: Diana Pretend Cooking With Cute Kitchen toys
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma Pretend Cooking With Cute Kitchen toys. Children are playing in cafe. This is a pretend play cafe which has lots of delicious food! Diana's cafe just opened and her first visitor came to her. But suddenly a competitor appears - brother Roma also opened his cafe. Kids cooking the most delicious dishes to please the only visitor and lure him to themselves.
